title: Narcotics Anonymous Ultimate Collection
description:
This is a comprehensive collection of Narcotics Anonymous & recovery material. It contains:
1. Basic Text audio files
2. Basic Text (Fifth Edition PDF & Word versions)
3. It Works How and Why (PDF & Word versions)
4. Living Clean (approval draft)
5. Step Working Guide (PDF & Word versions)
6. Twelve templates for working each steps using the questions from the Step Working Guide (Word format)
7. NA White Booklet
8. The Grey Book (unpublished and unauthorized)
9. Just for Today (PDF & Word)
10. All other NA Fellowship-approved literature including IP's and Group Readings.
11. AA literature (The Big Book & Twelve Steps and Twelve Traditions)
12. A Buddhist's Insight into the 12 Steps of Recovery
